message.body: Hi Sheridan. How's life? I'm getting my hair done and ain't got nuffin to do.

Haha, life is getting better! Everything yesterday with Logan is done with on my part, after a couple texts I just ignored him. Drinking coffee and watching meet the Robinson's.. I love this movie. Watcha doing to your hair?
Marvelous! Sometimes it sucks but you just gotta finish one chapter to move on to the next. Also that movie is da bomb diggity
